This paper deals with analyzing the behavior of users and conversations in WhatsApp groups, which involves social interactions and cybersecurity aspects. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.SI (Social and Information Networks), followed by cs.SOC (Social and Behavioral Sciences), cs.CYBER (Cybersecurity and Privacy), cs.CR (Cryptography and Security), and cs.IR (Information Retrieval).
